{"tid":2446923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla今晚好撚大鑊 中央將於315晚會全國直播公審Tesla","createTime":"2021-03-14T22:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T15:55:02.000Z","uid":391580,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"24b5552d41f288476056dd0c94b929dc12ca4e11","tid":2446923,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SXfkfv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SXfkfv.jpg&h=45118049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中央廣播電視總台3&middot;15晚會為中國中央廣播電視總台與中國政府相關部門、中國消費者協會共同主辦的晚會，自1991年起每年固定在國際消費者權益日3月15日晚上播出（2020年因2019冠狀病毒病延期到同年7月播出），通過揭露和曝光社會生活中的侵犯消費者權益的事例，幾乎每個上315晚會的被公審公司在市場都會遭受嚴重的打擊，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">在中國被稱為令企業聞之色變的節目<br />\n<br />\n今年特斯拉在中國發生多起意外，幾乎已經肯定315晚會中必定會被中共公審</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXSV4He.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXSV4He.jpg&h=359f2642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ctee.com.tw/news/china/429648.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fctee.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F429648.html&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2aac707c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ctee.com.tw/news/china/429648.html</a><br />\n<br />\n特斯拉在中國近日成為了最熱門的新聞話題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdmjMWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdmjMWz.jpg&h=817fdf0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5056645ee23d6162df4d5fc2510cc8cb83f95b79","tid":2446923,"uid":391580,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Me8qHyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMe8qHyV.jpg&h=df8c5f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1j10kB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1j10kB.jpg&h=72acbffe&s={SI